import "./style/ProjectsPage.css" import "./style/General.css" import { Link } from "react-router-dom"; import NavBar from "./NavBar"; const ProjectsPage = () => { const projects = require("./../projects.json") return (
{/*

Voxel Carving

June 2022

Voxel Carving is a 3D reconstruction project that converts images of an object (taken from different camera views) and creates a 3D representation.

D@B

April 2022

D@B (Dorms at Brown) is a site designed to give Brown students access to information about each dorm on campus (pictures, features, reviews, etc) in order to help them make decisions during the housing process.

Under the Sea

December 2021

Under the Sea is a project the displays an underwater scene incorporating features such as procedurally generated terrain, corals, and camera movement along bezier curves.

*/}
) } export default ProjectsPage;
